sic\">\n{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nichole-nordeman-mn0000396144/awards |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6O6PdSV9k?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nichole-nordeman-mn0000396144/awards |title=Nichole Nordeman Awards |work=Allmusic |publisher=All Media Network |accessdate=March 16, 2014 |archivedate=March 15, 2014 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"Albums \u2013 Billboard 200\">\n''Billboard'' 200 chart positions for all albums: {{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=Nichole Nordeman|chart=Billboard 200}} |title=Nichole Nordeman Album & Song Chart History: The Billboard 200 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]] |accessdate=March 16, 2014 }}<br />\nExcept for:\n* ''Music Inspired by The Story'': {{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6O6T2kQZz?url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/search/charts?f%5B0%5D=is_bmdb_album_id:338348&f%5B1%5D=itm_field_chart_id:305&refine=1 |title=Music Inspired by The Story Album Performance |work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |accessdate=March 16, 2014 |archivedate=March 16, 2014 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"Albums \u2013 Billboard Christian Albums\">\n''Billboard'' Christian Albums chart positions for all albums: \n{{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=Nichole Nordeman|chart=Christian Albums}} |title=Nichole Nordeman Album & Song Chart History: Christian Albums |work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |accessdate=March 16, 2014 }}\nExcept for:\n* ''Music Inspired by The Story'': {{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6O6Syvok5?url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/search/charts?f%5B0%5D=ss_chart_search_title:%22Music%20Inspired%20By%20The%20Story%22&f%5B1%5D=itm_field_chart_id:310&refine=1 |title=Music Inspired by The Story Album Performance  |work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |accessdate=March 16, 2014 |archivedate=March 16, 2014 }}\n</ref>\n<ref nam