ragile]]'' (Nothing)\n* [[Smash Mouth]] - ''[[Astro Lounge]]''\n* Various artists - ''[[Wild Wild West (soundtrack)]]''\n\n== 2000s ==\n\n=== 2000 ===\n* [[2Pac]] - ''[[The Rose That Grew from Concrete]]''\n* [[The Black Eyed Peas]] - ''[[Bridging the Gap (Black Eyed Peas album)|Bridging the Gap]]'' (will.i.am Music Group)\n* [[Vanessa Carlton]] - ''[[A Thousand Miles]]''\n* [[Drag-On]] - ''[[Opposite of H2O]]'' (Ruff Ryderse)\n* [[Eminem]] - ''[[The Marshall Mathers LP]]'' (Aftermath)\n* [[Jurassic 5]] - ''[[Quality Control (album)|Quality Control]]''\n* [[Limp Bizkit]] - ''[[Chocolate Starfish and the Hot Dog Flavored Water]]''\n* [[The LOX]] - ''[[We Are the Streets]]'' (Ruff Ryders)\n* [[Marilyn Manson]] - ''[[Holy Wood (In the Shadow of the Valley of Death)]]'' (Nothing)\n* [[No Doubt]] - ''[[Return of Saturn]]''\n* [[Queens of the Stone Age]] - ''[[Rated R (Queens of the Stone Age album)|Rated R]]''\n* [[U2]] - ''[[All That You Can't Leave Behind]]'' ([[Island Records]])\n\n=== 2001 ===\n* [[2Pac]] - ''[[Until the End of Time (Tupac Shakur album)|Until the End of Time]]'' \n* [[D12]] - ''[[Devil's Night]]'' (Shady)\n* [[Eve (entertainer)|Eve]] - ''[[Scorpion (Eve album)|Scorpion]]'' (Ruff Ryders)\n* [[Jadakiss]] - ''[[Kiss tha Game Goodbye]]'' (Ruff Ryders)\n* [[Limp Bizkit]] - ''[[New Old Songs]]''\n* [[No Doubt]] - ''[[Rock Steady (album)|Rock Steady]]''\n* [[Smash Mouth]] - ''[[Smash Mouth (album)|Smash Mouth]]''\n* Various artists - ''[[Ali (film)|Ali (soundtrack)]]''\n* Various artists - ''[[The Wash (soundtrack)]]''\n\n=== 2002 ===\n* [[2Pac]] - ''[[Better Dayz]]''\n* [[...And You Will Know Us by the Trail of Dead|...And You Will Know Us By The Trail of Dead]] - ''[[Source Tags & Codes]]''\n* [[Eminem]] - ''[[The Eminem Show]]'' (Shady/Aftermath)\n* [[Jurassic 5]] - ''[[Power in Numbers]]''\n* [[Styles P]] - ''[[A Gangster and a Gentleman]]'' (Ruff Ryders)\n* [[Truth Hurts (singer)|Truth Hurts]] - ''[[Truthfully Speaking]]'' (Aftermath)\n* [[t.A.T.u.]] -