 album)|Redemption]]'' (Top Dawg)\n* Billy Raffoul - ''1975''\n* Colouring - ''bn''\n* Moneybagg Yo - ''Bet On Me'' (N-Less)\n* [[Bas (rapper)|Bas]] - ''[[Milky Way (album)|Milky Way]] (Dreamville)\n* [[Eminem]] - ''[[Kamikaze (Eminem album)|Kamikaze]]'' (Shady/Aftermath)\n* [[The Night Game]] - ''The Night Game'' (Real Johnson/Vertigo/Capitol)\n* Trill Sammy - ''No Sleep Vol. 1'' (Mad Love)\n* Yoshi Flower - ''Brown Paper Bag (Maxi)'' (Rock Mafia/GRDN)\n* [[Pale Waves]] - ''[[My Mind Makes Noises]]'' (Dirty Hit)\n* [[6LACK]] - ''[[East Atlanta Love Letter]]'' (LVRN)\n* [[Machine Gun Kelly (rapper)|Machine Gun Kelly]] - [[Binge (EP)|BINGE]]\n* [[Lady Gaga]] & [[Bradley Cooper]] - [[A Star Is Born (2018 soundtrack)|A Star Is Born (soundtrack)]]\n* [[Sheck Wes]] - ''[[Mudboy (album)|MUDBOY]]'' (Cactus Jack/GOOD)\n* [[Ella Mai]] - ''[[Ella Mai (album)|Ella Mai]]'' (10 Summers)\n* Yoshi Flower - ''AMERICAN RAVER'' (Rock Mafia/GRDN)\n* [[Future (rapper)|Future]] & Juice WRLD - ''[[Wrld on Drugs]]'' (Grade A/Freebandz/Epic)\n* [[Lil Mosey]] - ''[[Northsbest]]''\n* [[Summer Walker]] - ''[[Last Day of Summer (Summer Walker album)|Last Day of Summer]]'' (LVRN)\n* [[Louis the Child (DJs)|Louis the Child]] - ''Kids At Play''\n* [[The Struts]] - ''[[Young & Dangerous (album)|YOUNG&DANGEROUS]]''\n* Tory Lanez - ''[[Love Me Now?|LoVE me NOw]]'' (Mad Love)\n* [[Jacob Banks]] - ''Village'' (Darkroom)\n* [[Jay Critch]] - ''Hood Favorite'' (Rich Forever)\n* [[K Camp]] - ''RARE Sound'' (RARE Sound/EMPIRE)\n* [[Kris Wu]] - ''[[Antares (album)|Antares]]'' (Ace Unit/Go East/Universal Music China)\n* [[Smino]] - ''[[Noir (Smino album)|N\u00d8IR]]'' (Zero Fatigue/Downtown)\n* [[Imagine Dragons]] - ''[[Origins (Imagine Dragons album)|Origins]]'' (KIDinaKORNER)\n* [[Lil Durk]] - ''Signed To The Streets 3'' (Only The Family/Alamo)\n* [[Nightly (band)|Nightly]] - ''The Sound Of Your Voice''\n* [[Mike Will Made It|Mike WiLL Made-It]] - ''[[Creed II (soundtrack)|Creed II: The Album]]'' (Eardruma